FormFiles.ScheduleForms

Class AddDropOffForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • FormFiles.ScheduleForms.AddDropOffForm

  • public class AddDropOffForm
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to add a drop off to the trucks schedule through a user interface to display the information. Based on trucks current location and the list of packages currently associated with the trucks to figure out which orders need to be dropped off. Only works with the order's target location being the current location of the truck
    Since:
    2/24/2021
